# https://api.flutter.dev/javadoc/io/flutter/embedding/android/FlutterActivity.html
# FlutterActivity
Package [io.flutter.embedding.android](package-summary.html)

### withNewEngine
@NonNull
public static [FlutterActivity.NewEngineIntentBuilder](FlutterActivity.NewEngineIntentBuilder.html) withNewEngine()
Creates an [`FlutterActivity.NewEngineIntentBuilder`](FlutterActivity.NewEngineIntentBuilder.html), which can be used to configure an [`Intent`](https://developer.android.com/reference/android/content/Intent.html) to
 launch a `FlutterActivity` that internally creates a new [`FlutterEngine`](../engine/FlutterEngine.html) using the desired Dart entrypoint, initial route,
 etc.

Returns:
The engine intent builder.

