### onCreate
protected void onCreate(@Nullable
 [Bundle](https://developer.android.com/reference/android/os/Bundle.html) savedInstanceState)

Overrides:
`[onCreate](https://developer.android.com/reference/android/app/Activity.html#onCreate(android.os.Bundle))` in class `[Activity](https://developer.android.com/reference/android/app/Activity.html)`

